 <h2 id="head-55f8ebc805e65b5b71ddafdae390e3be2bcd69af">Description</h2>
A module for ToME that tries to get even closer to Tolkien roots. Not canonical or chronologically accurate by any stretch of imagination; like ToME, it combines Ages and personalities and stories, and introduces some `ideas' - for example, what happened to the Ithryn Luin and Elenwe, who is Tom Bombadil, were Glorfindel of Gondolin and Glorfindel of Rivendell the same person, and other points of contention in canon. <p>
Theme introduces a completely new and more dangerous wilderness map, over 200 new monsters (plus 59 uniques), no Zangband or Cthangband monsters (activating those options does nothing), many new artifacts, objects, and ego items, new gods to worship, new character races, subraces, and subclasses, as well as changes to some existing races and classes. 
</p>
<h3 id="head-06b7ee09b1fffdd88ebc899e58278bebdc4ab538">In this version</h3>
<p>
This is a a bugfix/update release with some documentation updates, as well as a number of race, class, and God tweaks. 
</p>
<p>
There are currently two simultaneous versions of Theme - one for ToME 2.2.7 and one for the 2.3.0 CVS version. 
</p>
<p>
You can get more information at the <a class="external" href=".www.zionmainframe.ca/tome/theme/"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-www.png" alt="[WWW]" height="11" width="11">Theme site</a>. 
</p>
<h2 id="head-a69ab6442fa5e4ed9de9974074737205958697f1">Module Version</h2>
1.1.0 a.k.a "Forever There" <h2 id="head-c0975d85796fcb5ef3b4bf9d9c2388a4b1dc8123">T-Engine version</h2>
2.2.7 / 2.3.0(CVS) <h2 id="head-5fda23d62015b99fb2a9f86b38bcdf2bdf7609c8">Author</h2>
<a href="./FuriousOne">FuriousOne</a> <h2 id="head-cf1b91677c424704e7d3a429fb90869242e87885">Last update</h2>
11/10/2004 <h2 id="head-a479c9c34e878d07b4d67a73a48f432ad7dc53c8">Download</h2>
You can download this module as a <a class="external" href=".modules.t-o-m-e.net/mods/28__theme.zip"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-www.png" alt="[WWW]" height="11" width="11">zip file</a>. (size: 999kB) If you want to play the module with the 2.3.0(CVS) version of ToME, please download at the <a class="external" href=".www.zionmainframe.ca/tome/theme/theme.zip"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-www.png" alt="[WWW]" height="11" width="11">Theme site</a> instead. (size: 1 015 kB) <p>
The graphical tiles are available as a separate download at the <a class="external" href=".www.zionmainframe.ca/tome/theme/graf.zip"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-www.png" alt="[WWW]" height="11" width="11">Theme site - 727Kb</a>. Note that the pref files distributed with Theme are already configured to work with the Theme tiles. 
</p>
