<p>
<a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./BugReports#head-a797e30923ac1be590300ce6b08e63b4e6dc6688"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Theme bugs</a> 
